 RвҶҗTEST_SVG;SVG;CX;CY;RAD;N
вҚқ Test PLOTSVG generates valid SVG markup
вҚқ Runs after standard pipeline setup (Anaheim 1974 test case)
 RвҶҗ1

вҚқ Set observation parameters (same as EXAMPLE_RENDER)
 STATEDDAYNOвҶҗJNU 5 16 1974
 STATEDTIMEвҶҗ5
 LONGвҶҗВҜ117.833
 LATвҶҗ33.767
 TIMEвҶҗLONG TIMEADJUST STATEDTIME
 DATEвҶҗSTATEDDAYNO+(TIMEГ·24)-LONGГ·360
 CALCULATEPLANETS
 CALCULATESTARS

вҚқ Generate SVG
 SVGвҶҗPLOTSVG

вҚқ Must return a character vector
 :If ~(1=вҚҙвҚҙSVG)вҲ§(''вүЎ0вҚҙSVG)
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: PLOTSVG must return a character vector'
   RвҶҗ0
   :Return
 :EndIf

вҚқ Must be non-empty
 :If 0=вүўSVG
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: PLOTSVG returned empty string'
   RвҶҗ0
   :Return
 :EndIf

вҚқ Must start with SVG tag (possibly with XML declaration)
 :If ~вҲЁ/'<svg 'вҚ·SVG
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: no <svg element found'
   RвҶҗ0
 :EndIf

вҚқ Must close the SVG tag
 :If ~вҲЁ/'</svg>'вҚ·SVG
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: no closing </svg> tag'
   RвҶҗ0
 :EndIf

вҚқ Must contain viewBox with 2320 width (2160 + 2Г—80 padding)
 :If ~вҲЁ/'viewBox="0 0 2320'вҚ·SVG
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: viewBox width not 2320 (2160 + padding)'
   RвҶҗ0
 :EndIf

вҚқ Must contain horizon circle (cx=1080 cy=1080 r=1080)
 :If ~вҲЁ/'id="horizon"'вҚ·SVG
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: no horizon circle element'
   RвҶҗ0
 :EndIf

вҚқ Must contain crosshairs
 :If ~вҲЁ/'id="crosshairs"'вҚ·SVG
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: no crosshairs element'
   RвҶҗ0
 :EndIf

вҚқ Must contain cardinal direction labels
 :If ~(вҲЁ/'>N<'вҚ·SVG)вҲ§(вҲЁ/'>S<'вҚ·SVG)вҲ§(вҲЁ/'>E<'вҚ·SVG)вҲ§(вҲЁ/'>W<'вҚ·SVG)
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: missing cardinal direction labels'
   RвҶҗ0
 :EndIf

вҚқ Must contain star circles вҖ” at least as many as visible stars
 NвҶҗ+/'<circle 'вҚ·SVG
 :If N<+/VE
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: only ',(вҚ•N),' <circle elements, expected at least ',(вҚ•+/VE)
   RвҶҗ0
 :EndIf

вҚқ Must contain bright star labels вҖ” check a few known names
 :If ~вҲЁ/'Arcturus'вҚ·SVG
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: bright star label Arcturus not found'
   RвҶҗ0
 :EndIf
 :If ~вҲЁ/'Vega'вҚ·SVG
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: bright star label Vega not found'
   RвҶҗ0
 :EndIf

вҚқ Must contain planet symbols for visible planets
 :If ~вҲЁ/'class="planet"'вҚ·SVG
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: no planet elements found'
   RвҶҗ0
 :EndIf

вҚқ Must contain planet report table
 :If ~вҲЁ/'POSITION OF SUN, MOON AND PLANETS'вҚ·SVG
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: planet table header not found'
   RвҶҗ0
 :EndIf

вҚқ Must contain moon phase line
 :If ~вҲЁ/'MOON PHASE'вҚ·SVG
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: moon phase line not found'
   RвҶҗ0
 :EndIf

вҚқ Must contain bright star table
 :If ~вҲЁ/'BRIGHT STARS'вҚ·SVG
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: bright star table not found'
   RвҶҗ0
 :EndIf

 :If R
   вҺ•вҶҗ'PASS: TEST_SVG (',(вҚ•вүўSVG),' chars, ',(вҚ•+/VE),' stars, ',(вҚ•+/VP),' planets)'
 :EndIf
